WEBVTT

00:11.089 --> 00:12.123
- _
- You're not up to it.

00:12.167 --> 00:13.088
You're not a sheriff.

00:13.090 --> 00:13.936
(GUNSHOT)

00:13.938 --> 00:16.772
You should stay here. If
you move, you could bleed.

00:16.774 --> 00:19.296
It's a psychological
reaction to the wasp trauma.

00:19.340 --> 00:20.884
So I'm not blind, I'm just mental?

00:20.933 --> 00:22.780
I understand how upset you are.

00:22.829 --> 00:24.740
This is not my dream job.

00:24.772 --> 00:26.536
I need to find Governor Odegard.

00:26.591 --> 00:31.040
There was a disaster,
1942, near Vukobejina.

00:31.101 --> 00:33.164
Something about regeneration.

00:33.214 --> 00:37.004
- They could reverse tissue damage?
- They hurt him and he healed.

00:38.675 --> 00:39.628
(CAPSULE CLATTERS)

00:40.799 --> 00:42.842
(GRUNTING)

00:44.999 --> 00:49.137
♪ The river did come to me ♪

00:49.175 --> 00:52.702
♪ Straight into my arms ♪

00:54.157 --> 00:57.709
